	<h3>input</h3>
	- 데이터를 입력받는 태그<br>
	- type속성에 따라 형식이 달라진다<br>
	<input type="button" value="버 튼"><br>
	<input type="submit" value="서브밋"><br>
	<input type="reset" value="초기화"><br>
	<input type="image" value="img.jpg" width="50"><br>
	<input type="file"><br>
	
	<input type="text" value="값 입력"><br>
	<input type="password" value="비밀번호"><br>
	<input type="email" placeholder="text@test.t"><br>
	<input type="search" value="값 입력시x버튼 생성"><br>
	<input type="tel" value="010-555-555"><br>
	<input type="number" min="1" max="10" value="1"><br>
	
	<input type="color"><br>
	<input type="range"><br>
	<input type="radio"><br>
	<input type="checkbox"><br>
	<input type="hidden" value="값을 숨김"><br>
	<input type="text" value="읽기전용" readonly="readonly"><br>

